title: 09/12: Buy Low/Sell High; PIT RBs; Regulators; BAL-CIN (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
So much to discuss on today's show including Carson Wentz's value, a player we forgot to mention yesterday, some sneaky add/drops we made and the latest news from around the NFL ... Let's talk about those PIT RBs! What do you do with Le'Veon Bell and James Conner? What are their values in redraft and keeper leagues? Then we tell you early round picks we're concerned about, players we don't want to give up on and some buy low and sell high candidates ... BAL-CIN preview, "Buy Low or Heck No," "Sell High or No Thanks, Guy" and Fantasy Regulators! ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
